{"type":null,"faqId":14004,"title":"拍照时能否记录位置信息？","answer":"<p>\n  <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">使用荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">拍照时，可以将拍照地点的位置信息添加到所拍摄的照片中。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span>1.<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在主屏幕界面，点击<b>设置</b></span><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">全部设置</span></b><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">定位服务</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span>2.<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">勾选</span><b><span>GPS</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卫星</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，开启</span><span>GPS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卫星定位功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=44719\" width=\"529\" height=\"476\" alt=\"\" /></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span>&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span>3.<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在主屏幕界面，点击</span> <b><span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=44720\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" alt=\"\" /></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">相机</span></b><span> &gt; <b><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=44721\" width=\"29\" height=\"21\" alt=\"\" /></b>&nbsp;&gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">其他</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，勾选<b>地理信息</b>。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">使用荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">拍摄照片后，您可以在照片浏览界面点击</span> <b><span><b style=\"white-space:normal;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=44721\" width=\"29\" height=\"21\" alt=\"\" /></b></span></b><span>&nbsp;&gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">详细信息</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">中查看该照片的位置信息。</span>\n</p>","faqTypeId":167,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5664","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Camera-Picture","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1406077197000,"seriesProductName":"7D-501u","visitedTimes":78,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"拍照,照相,位置,地点、坐标、定位","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}